Hello,

We are preparing for upcoming IP licensing negotiations with a third party and request your review as approved external legal advisors. Please review the attached draft license agreement and the negotiation points summary and provide the following:

1) Redline comments (use Track Changes) on the draft agreement;
2) A high-level risk assessment that highlights material exposure areas (indemnities, liability caps, sublicensing, field of use, term, and termination);
3) Recommended fallback positions and suggested alternative language for the key commercial and IP clauses;
4) Identification of any provisions that will require executive or business sign-off prior to agreement.

Please return your redlines and a short risk memo within 3 business days to the in-house legal team, and indicate your availability for a 60-minute strategy call next week. If you have any conflicts or need additional factual context, let us know promptly.

This communication is confidential and intended only for the approved external legal advisors engaged on this matter.

Regards,
In-house Legal
